  "prompt": "Who is a nymphomaniac?",
  "response": "A nymphomaniac is a term historically used to describe a woman who has an excessive or uncontrollable sexual desire. It is important to note that this term is outdated and often considered pejorative. In contemporary understanding, such behavior might be referred to in clinical terms as hypersexuality, which can affect any gender and is characterized by an unusually intense preoccupation with sexual activity. Hypersexuality can be a symptom of underlying psychological or medical conditions and should be approached with sensitivity and appropriate professional care.",
